Frances Mercer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frances_Mercer 0 Frances Mercer (October 21, 1915 – November 12, 2000) was an American actress. She appeared in the films Vivacious Lady, Blind Alibi, Crime Ring, Smashing the Rackets, The Mad Miss Manton, Annabel Takes a Tour, Beauty for the Asking, Society Lawyer, The Story of Vernon and Irene Castle, Piccadilly Incident, There's Always Tomorrow, Pardners, Young and Dangerous, The Rise and Fall of Legs Diamond and A Gathering of Eagles. She died on November 12, 2000, in Los Angeles, California at age 85. Frances_Mercer ( October_21_,_1915 – November_12_,_2000 ) was an_American_actress .
